title: Winning Without A Huge Steph Game??
description:
In this edition of Debatable After Dark, Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Spencer Hall debate how significant it is that the Warriors won without a big Steph game and what they think of Andrew Wiggins at this point.
